; Wunderlich &amp; MÃ¼ller, 2018). 
<taxonomicName id="B1D04D4FFFD3FFFEBCACFD73143FFD03" authority="Jiang &amp; Li" authorityName="Jiang &amp; Li" box="[218,528,652,676]" class="Arachnida" family="Pilosarachnidae" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="2" pageNumber="268" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Pilosarachnidae Jiang &amp; Li</taxonomicName>
, 
<emphasis id="44A4EADEFFD3FFFEBE56FD7314A0FD03" bold="true" box="[544,655,652,676]" pageId="2" pageNumber="268">fam. nov.</emphasis>
resembles â€  
